{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/pages/nodejs-install","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ij.Log"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"nvm-node-version-manager\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nvm-node-version-manager\" aria-label=\"nvm node version manager permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>NVM (Node Version Manager)</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm\">NVM (Node Version Manager)</a> 란 Node.js의 버전을 관리하는 도구이다. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>협업, 다양한 프로젝트를 동시에 진행해야 할 때</li>\n<li>컴퓨터에 다양한 버전의 node.js를 설치할 때\n등의 상황에 이점이 있으며, 커맨드로 간단하게 node 버전을 스위칭할 수 있다. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>나의 경우에는 리눅스에 node.js 를 설치하면 지나치게 하위 버전이 설치되는 문제가 계속 발생해 nvm 으로 node.js 를 설치하게 되었다. (편하다)</p>\n<h2 id=\"nvm-install\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nvm-install\" aria-label=\"nvm install permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>NVM Install</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">// <span class=\"token function\">curl</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.36.0/install.sh <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">bash</span> \n\n// <span class=\"token function\">wget</span> \n<span class=\"token function\">wget</span> -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.36.0/install.sh <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">bash</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">// .bashrc 설정 리로드\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> ~/.bashrc</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nvm <span class=\"token function\">install</span> node    <span class=\"token comment\"># 최신버전 설치</span>\nnvm <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --lts   <span class=\"token comment\"># lts 설치</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"그-외-nvm-command\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8-%EC%99%B8-nvm-command\" aria-label=\"그 외 nvm command permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>그 외 NVM command</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 설치된 node.js 목록 확인하기</span>\n$ nvm <span class=\"token function\">ls</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 설치할 수 있는 Node 버전 조회</span>\n$ nvm ls-remote\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 특정 버전의 node 사용하기</span>\n$ nvm use <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>version<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 현재 사용중인 버전 확인하기</span>\n$ nvm current\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># node.js 설치 경로 확인하기</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">which</span> node\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 필요없는 node 버전 삭제하기</span>\n$ nvm uninstall <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>version<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","excerpt":"NVM (Node Version Manager) NVM (Node Version Manager) 란 Node.js의 버전을 관리하는 도구이다.  협업, 다양한 프로젝트를 동시에 진행해야 할 때 컴퓨터에 다양한 버전의 node.js…","frontmatter":{"date":"2010-10-13","title":"[Node.js NVM을 이용하여 Node.js 설치","tags":["Node.js","dev env"],"keywords":["Node.js","node 버전 관리"]},"fields":{"slug":"/pages/nodejs-install"},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/pages/nodejs-install/#nvm-node-version-manager\">NVM (Node Version Manager)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/pages/nodejs-install/#nvm-install\">NVM Install</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/pages/nodejs-install/#%EA%B7%B8-%EC%99%B8-nvm-command\">그 외 NVM command</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/pages/nodejs-install"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2827402515","694178885"]}